summary:
OpenLeverage Launches Mainnet on Ethereum - OpenLeverage brings DeFi protocols, yield aggregators, the LSD Protocol, wallets, chains, and various tools together to create a thriving and open ecosystem.

 OpenLeverage Completed Security Audit With PeckShield - Built with security as our highest priority.

 OpenLeverage Testnet V2 Goes Alive - The OpenLeverage token OLE is live! It will become transferable upon further announcement.
